# 📘 Relation-aware Fusion Risk Perception Network (RFRP-Net)

**Dynamic Risk Analysis and Anomaly Detection in Supply Chain Networks**

---

## 🧩 Overview
This repository contains the implementation of **RFRP-Net (Relation-aware Fusion Risk Perception Network)** —  
a deep learning framework for **dynamic supply chain risk prediction and anomaly detection**.

RFRP-Net integrates:
- A **Relation-Aware Graph Convolutional Network (RA-GCN)** for heterogeneous structural modeling.
- An **Attention-based Abnormality Detection Feature Fusion (AADFF)** mechanism for anomaly perception.

> 📄 This repository accompanies the paper:  
> *“Relation-aware Fusion Risk Perception Network for Dynamic Risk Analysis and Anomaly Detection in Supply Chain Networks”*

---

