Stay tuned — the initial release is expected soon.

---

## 🔍 Model Architecture
RFRP-Net consists of two major components:

1. **Relation-Aware Graph Convolutional Network (RA-GCN)**  
   Captures heterogeneous relationships among customers, orders, and products using multi-granularity attention guided by business similarity and risk intensity.

2. **Attention-based Abnormality Detection Feature Fusion (AADFF)**  
   Enhances weak anomaly detection through sparsity- and deviation-constrained query vectors, Bi-LSTM encoding, and attention entropy metrics.

---

## 🗂️ Dataset
Experiments are based on the **DataCo Global Supply Chain Dataset**, which includes operational data from supply, production, sales, and distribution stages.  
Due to licensing and size constraints, the dataset is **not included** here.  
You can download it from Figshare:  
🔗 [https://doi.org/10.6084/m9.figshare.28714328](https://doi.org/10.6084/m9.figshare.28714328)

### Data Preprocessing (to be released)
The preprocessing script will:
- Construct a dynamic heterogeneous graph  
- Apply **Min–Max normalization** to numerical features  
- Perform **One-hot encoding** on categorical features  
- Generate **temporal snapshots** for dynamic modeling

